| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0911 — Recovery Inhibition (play)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 7cc9dee3-7803-51ad-9e6a-6b8e0e25f62c"
